Alô?

106
00:10:19,342 --> 00:10:20,551
Não.

107
00:10:30,799 --> 00:10:31,842
Alô?

108
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:36,467
<i>Cornish.</i>

109
00:10:53,092 --> 00:10:54,259
Entre.

110
00:10:57,718 --> 00:10:58,842
Sente-se.

111
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,175
Ela está ali?

112
00:11:08,967 --> 00:11:09,800
Não.

113
